Yayin da Sin ke kara kaimi wajen bunkasa fasahar kere-kere, Amurka na bukatar ta ninka yawan kudaden da take kashewa wajen bincike kan wannan fannin, a cewar mai binciken fasahar kere-kere Kai-Foo Li, wanda ya yi aiki a Google da Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan na zuwa ne bayan da sassan gwamnatin Amurka suka fitar da wasu sanarwa game da AI, duk da cewa gwamnatin Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar AI.
A halin da ake ciki, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirinta a shekarar da ta gabata: burinta na zama na farko a fannin ilimin kere-kere nan da shekarar 2030.
"Karuwar kasafin kudin bincike a fannin ilimin kere kere na zamani zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, ganin cewa duk sauran kasashe suna da nisa a baya ga Amurka, kuma muna neman wata sabuwar fasahar kere kere ta zamani", in ji Li.
"Idan aka ninka kudaden da aka bayar, za a ninka damar da za a samu na samar da wata babbar fasaha mai kwakwalwa a Amurka", in ji Li a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Li, wanda littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order ya fito a wannan watan a Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne shugaban kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a kamfanin fasaha na zamani na kasar Sin, Face++ .
A cikin shekarun 1980s a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin ilimin artificial wanda ya ci nasara a wasan kwallon kafa na farko a Amurka, kuma daga baya ya zama babban jami'in Microsoft Research kuma shugaban reshen Google a China.
Na san da wasu gasa da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi a baya, kamar su Hukumar Bincike ta Duniya ta Robotics Challenge, kuma na tambaye su yaushe za a yi na gaba, don a taimaka a gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
Masu bincike a Amurka sukan yi aiki tuƙuru don samun tallafin gwamnati, in ji shi.
"Ba China ce ke janye mana manyan malamai daga makarantun ba, kamfanoni ne ke yin hakan", in ji shi.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha a shekarun baya sun dauki taurari daga jami'a don yin aiki a fannin ilimin kere kere.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauye a manufofin shige da fice na iya taimaka wa Saudiyya wajen inganta ayyukanta a fannin ilimin kere kere.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da izinin zama na dindindin ga masu digiri na biyu a fannin ilimin kere kere", in ji shi.
A watan Yuli na shekarar 2017, majalisar zartarwa ta kasar Sin ta fitar da shirin bunkasa fasahar kere-kere ta zamani.
Asusun Kimiyyar Kimiyya na kasar Sin yana ba da tallafi ga mutane a cibiyoyin ilimi kamar yadda Asusun Kimiyyar Kimiyya na kasar Sin da sauran hukumomin gwamnati suke ba da tallafi ga masu bincike a Amurka, amma ingancin aikin ilimi a kasar Sin ya fi ƙasa da ƙasa, in ji ni.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa wata cibiyar hada-hadar fasaha ta wucin gadi, wadda aka tsara don hada masana'antu da masana kimiyya, kuma fadar White House ta sanar da kafa wata kwamiti ta musamman kan fasahar kere-kere.
