Tallafin da China ta yi amfani da shi a matsayin wani mataki na ramuwar gayya a farkon yakin cinikayya, an yi shi ne don a yi wa 'yan kasuwa a wasu jihohi kamar Iowa da suka goyi bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican, a cewar masana Amurka da na China.
