Michaelson ya yi rashin nasara a wasan kuma ya sauka a benci a lokacin gasar Ryder a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan golf na Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa tarihi a ranar Lahadi da zai buga wasa na 47 a gasar Ryder, amma zai bukaci ya kara yawan wasanni domin kada wasan ya zama abin takaici.
Michaelson, wanda ya halarci taron shekara-shekara na 12th kuma ya kafa rikodin, ya sauka daga benen ta hanyar yanke shawara ta Jim Furyk yayin wasannin furball da foursomes a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon kasancewa a tsakiyar wasan, kamar yadda ya saba a wasannin da ya buga da tawagar 'yan wasan Amurka, Michaelson, wanda ya lashe gasar MLB sau biyar, ya shafe rabin rana a matsayin mai karfafawa da sauran rabin a kan wasan da yake yi a gefe da fatan ya gyara rashin lafiyar da yake fama da shi.
Ko da a lokacin da ya fi kowa tsada, wasan kwaikwayon ya sha wahala. Saboda haka, Michaelson mai shekaru 48 ba shine zaɓi mafi kyau ga wasan golf na National ba, inda dogon filin wasan ba ya yawanci ga masu yin wasan.
Kuma idan gasar ba ta da ban tsoro, Michaelson, a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi, ya yi nasara da zakaran zakarun Burtaniya, Francesco Molinari, wanda ya yi aiki tare da mai farawa Tommy Fleetwood kuma ya ci duk wasanninsu huɗu a wannan makon.
Idan burin 'yan Amirkawa, wanda ya rasa maki hudu a farkon wasanni 12 na farko, ya yi nasara a farkon matakan, wasan Mikaelson zai iya zama mai ƙayyadewa.
Furyk ya nuna amincewa da dan wasan nasa, ko da yake ba mu yi tsammanin zai ce wani abu ba.
"Ya fahimci aikinsa sosai a yau, ya taɓa bayana, ya ɗora hannunsa a kaina ya ce zai kasance a shirye gobe", in ji Furik.
