"Ina ci gaba da tunatar da kaina cewa muna da babbar nasara a Waldrama; cewa muna da babbar nasara a wasan Brooklyn, inda muka yi asara, kuma a Waldrama inda muka ci nasara amma da ɗan gajeren nasara", in ji Bjorn, a cikin hoton, bayan ya kalli nasarar 5-3 a gasar 2018 a ranar da kuma a jiya, wanda ya kai ga nasara 10-6 a Gasar Golf ta Duniya.
