Palo ne babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke a gefen wani bay a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da yawan jama'a kimanin 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Garin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa a lokacin da tsunami da girgizar kasa suka addabe shi.
Donggala shi ne gundumar da ke da fiye da kilomita 300 na gabar tekun a arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
Yawan jama'a a gundumar, yanki ne na yanki a cikin lardin, ya kai kimanin mutane 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Babban tushen samun kudin shiga a cikin tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya shine kamun kifi da noma, musamman a yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Wani muhimmin tushen samun kudin shiga shi ne hakar ma'adinai, wanda aka fi mayar da hankali a Murwalli, a gabar bakin tekun da ke gaba da Sulawesi.
Falo da Donggala sun fuskanci raƙuman tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'in Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Dongle.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa Donggala ta yamma a 1996 inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific Ring of Fire, wanda aka san shi da aikin girgizar ƙasa kuma ana yawan samun girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami da suka fi aukuwa a shekarun baya-bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a gabar tekun yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesiya a arewacin Sumatra, a ranar 26 ga Disamba, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya buge kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, kuma sama da rabin wadanda suka mutu sun mutu a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa a kudu da Java, mafi yawan tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a Indonesia, inda hakan ya haifar da tsunami da ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane kusan 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da garin Padanang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Sama da mutane 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata wasu ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa ta afkawa gundumar Fidi Ghayya da ke Azakhya, inda ta haifar da barna da fargaba, yayin da mazauna yankin suka tuna da lalacewar da ta biyo bayan mummunar girgizar kasa da guguwar tsunami a 2004.
Girgizar kasa ba ta haifar da tsunami a wannan yanayin ba, amma fiye da mutane 100 sun mutu a gine-ginen da suka rushe.
