Turai ta lashe kofin Ryder a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe Kofin Ryder na 2018 inda ta doke kungiyar Amurka da ci 16.5 - 10.5 a filin wasa na La Golf Nationale a waje da Paris, Faransa.
Amurka ta sha kashi a gasar Turai har sau shida a jere kuma ba ta lashe kofin Ryder ba tun shekarar 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambin a gasar yayin da tawagar Denmark ta Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata don cin Amurka.
Ba'amurke Phil Michelson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya kusan duk gasar, ya buga kwallo daga gefen T zuwa ruwa a rami na 16 na par-3, kuma ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Molinari ya yi fice a duk fafatawar da ya yi, kuma ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka kai 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a tsarin na yanzu, a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka, Gordon Spieth ya ci 5 da 4 a hannun dan wasan da ya fi kowacce daraja a Turai, Thorbjørn Olsen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, wanda shi ne dan wasan da ya fi kowane dan wasa a duniya, ya yi rashin nasara a wasan nan da ci biyu da daya a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda wataƙila shi ne zai yi wasa na ƙarshe a gasar Raiders.
Tare da tarihin halartar gasar Ryder Cup sau takwas, Spaniard Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan Turai da ya fi yawan nasara a gasar tare da maki 25.5.
